{"about_the_game":"<strong>Sorelle is a whimsical 3D puzzle-platformer that immerses you in the magical seaside town of Isola Chiara.</strong><br><br>Meet sisters Alessandra, Bella and Capri. Life in their seaside town goes astray when a violent storm destroys preparations for the annual summer festival and shatters the Duomo\u2019s stained glass, scattering the magic of the town. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916580/extras/SteamPageImg_03.png?t=1724655623\" /><br><br>The clock is ticking \u2014 the unrestrained magic seeks to return to the sea, the land, and the sky. Bestowed with fragments of this magic, the three sisters gain unique powers. Alessandra, the oldest and headstrong leader, harnesses the fluidity of the magic and gains the ability to levitate objects. Bella, the brash and brave middle sister, is granted strength to jump to new heights and break down obstacles. Capri, the curious and quiet youngest sister, is gifted with the ability to create light. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916580/extras/Sequence_01_13.gif?t=1724655623\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916580/extras/Sequence_01_15.gif?t=1724655623\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916580/extras/Sequence_01_14.gif?t=1724655623\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916580/extras/Sequence_01_16.gif?t=1724655623\" /><br><br>The sisters realize it's up to them to save the summer festival and restore magic to the town. Swap between the three playable sisters and combine their unique powers to solve puzzles, explore the village, and strengthen the bonds of sisterhood.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916580/extras/SteamPageImg_02.png?t=1724655623\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Includes</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>three Charming Playable Protagonists.<br></li><li>Dynamic puzzles that require creative use of every sisters\u2019 power.<br></li><li>Gorgeous and immersive Sicilian-inspired seaside scenery.<br></li><li>A heartwarming and family-centric story.<br></li><li>A whirling and magical original soundtrack.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916580/extras/SteamPageImg_04.png?t=1724655623\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Together Forever","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2916580/79ea9691d099150ac71d3d7e24cbe0e2f945ef89.jpg"},{"name":"Light Show","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2916580/5d34e49311c1665989d8acabe88a3a1b37045bc0.jpg"},{"name":"Gymnast","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2916580/080c31cf1f87c9202fb3703f01385a752ec8eaca.jpg"},{"name":"To The Sky","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2916580/1a5109af08f8c693eff0587be0a13868b61f0986.jpg"},{"name":"Organized","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2916580/f1deb191f4ce4100d3c065a137828c20b7854995.jpg"},{"name":"Lumare Lover","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2916580/7972770c9f08fa2e5564aac5a7f4f09700382978.jpg"},{"name":"A Moonlit Wonder","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2916580/34776bbef1b18fc9f27ca178bce1362477d99ade.jpg"},{"name":"Shattered Mysteries","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2916580/a91cc4a6e4f56aeba6533af1813221df49d5b23e.jpg"},{"name":"Three-of-a-Kind","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2916580/c4622b555b0c38c3760d6a10e25edf6963c8b009.j